snippet.title: Keshtat chibi animated trailer
snippet.description:
Keshtat is a role-playing game set in the future, where the AI’s commenced a rebellion against humanity and sought to conquer Qatar, and eventually, the world. 

Help us make this project come true by supporting us on Kickstarter! 

Kickstarter link: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/orionsreverie/keshtat
